===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|thank}}, from {{inh|en|ang|þanc||thought, favour, grace, pleasure, satisfaction, thanks}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*þankaz||thought, remembrance, gratitude}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*tong-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*teng-||to think}}. Cognate with {{cog|stq|Tonk}}, {{cog|fy|tank}}, {{cog|nl|dank}}, {{cog|nds|Dank}}, {{cog|de|Dank}}, {{cog|da|tak}}, {{cog|sv|tack}}, {{cog|fo|tøkk}}, {{cog|is|þökk}}. Related to {{m|en|thought}}.

